  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms</strong> are about 17m² and look out over the square. All Rooms have air conditioning, free Wi-Fi, TV and minibar.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are about 30m² and sleep up to four people. They're spacious and have a separate living area with sea views.</p>
<p><strong>Suites</strong> are about 37m² and sleep up to four people. They have sea views, a balcony or terrace and a raised sleeping area or separate living room.</p>
<p><strong>Standard Single</strong> <strong>Rooms</strong> are also available.</p>
<p>Please note that all rooms at the Hotel Fontana are available on a request basis, please call to book. Early booking is highly recommended.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
